main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted by several reliable witnesses at Big Springs, Texas on August 20, 1965.
interesting points: The sighting involved two objects, one stationary while the other was moving,The objects maneuvered without displaying characteristics typical of satellites,The sighting lasted for 5 minutes and 10 seconds,The witnesses were assured of their anonymity and requested not to be contacted during the investigation, The report suggests the objects may have been similar to meteors.
